OL,3,CAmber weather warnings in place for
OL,4,Cparts of Wales
OL,6,FThe warning covers Blaenau Gwent,
OL,7,FBridgend, Caerphilly, Carmarthenshire,
OL,8,FMerthyr Tydfil, Monmouthshire, Neath
OL,9,FPort Talbot, Powys, Rhondda Cynon Taf,
OL,10,FSwansea and Torfaen.
OL,12,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) is
OL,13,Fasking people to be vigilant and
OL,14,Fprepared as surface water issues are
OL,15,Fexpected.
OL,17,FNRW is calling on people to keep away
OL,18,Ffrom swollen riverbanks and not to
OL,19,Fdrive or walk through floodwater.
