OL,3,CAmber weather warnings in place for
OL,4,Cparts of Wales
OL,6,FShe added that, if flooding is
OL,7,Fforecast in your area, people should
OL,8,Fthink about preparing a flood kit with
OL,9,Fany important documents and
OL,10,Fmedication, moving your car to higher
OL,11,Fground and moving treasured
OL,12,Fpossessions upstairs or to a higher
OL,13,Fplace.
OL,15,F"We do not provide flood warnings for
OL,16,Fflooding from surface water, so it's
OL,17,Fimportant for everyone to know their
OL,18,Fflood risk," she continued.
